      "ADDED: 7 sortable columns (server-side)",
      "ADDED: StatusBadge for both ticketType and status",
      "ADDED: elapsedDays with color-coded warning (>=7 amber, >=14 red)",
      "ADDED: 'assigneeName' column for team lead's assignment overview"
